    "Tabulation of publication from Google Scholar indicated a six-times growth from 2460 in the 5 years between 2004 and 2008, to 18,000 in the years between 2018 and 2022.",
    "ESG research efforts are known to be inundated by large data volume; it was not surprising that ESG research efforts in finance literature that were supported by artificial intelligence (AI) techniques, stood to represent about one-fifth of the publications on ESG in finance in the latter five years.",
